# ÖTILLÖ Utö — Training Schedule (May 11 – June 6)

## Principles
- **Taper the last week** — don't arrive tired
- **Prioritize brick sessions** (swim→run back-to-back) since that's the core skill of swimrun
- **Address the cramping** — longer sessions with active electrolyte intake every 30–40 min
- **Arms-only swim training** — all pool sessions use paddles + pull buoy to mimic race conditions

